\" /> <br />\nGrammar都係熟能生巧既野,錯唔緊要,記得自己錯乜就得.同埋嘗試比自己英文既環境(英文介面,用英文諗野)久而久之就可以潛移默化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好怕同人講,我都係不斷咁試下同D鬼佬吹水,自然少少就ok.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d19ed0d6fd95a90d3c53e437539fefb91403c06","tid":174972,"uid":69794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:45:45.000Z","msg":"training"},{"pid":"b676f28060a63e6a7196527fe0efccb8e8c7845f","tid":174972,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:47:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>真心睇美劇 輕鬆睇 慢慢會入血</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nDSE到yr2果排試過，睇雙字幕，但要逐格停黎睇好無癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔需要逐格停黎睇,自己試下唔好放空耳仔,比心機聽,唔好淨睇字幕就得,唔需要太心急<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似D假ABC都係靠浸返黎姐,你腦個潛意識會幫你學習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03b81dc6ad0f4f7c9fd3415c39768a0d09f9feb0","tid":174972,"uid":34160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:49:24.000Z","msg":"買劍橋藍色綠色紅色好大本嗰啲<br />\n睇曬佢，背埋"},{"pid":"69aee3e1ee1625d10330cabb04eafd45e27112e5","tid":174972,"uid":66119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:53:07.000Z","msg":"語文好一定係浸出黎 除非你比好多心機<br />\nD人話睇英文新聞同簡單文章其實係有用 <br />\n但係英文差既一開始就覺得難 放棄左之後又呻英文差不停LOOP<br />\n最方便又有趣既就睇youtube，歐美戲同劇，一開始搵D中英字幕 覺得OK既試下純英文字幕，最後唔用咁睇"},{"pid":"ed4c9ec10a9f76d8e6938a1a12bfa48347c1c0a5","tid":174972,"uid":70369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:54:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同樓主情況一樣<br />\nYear 3 hd上去<br />\n但英文好屎 寫都還好<br />\n講就真係唔係好掂 <br />\n但gpa過3😂😂😂<br />\n英文應該都係得小學程度</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咩科 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fb9345d2062fc1f9669cfbfbde776fffddcf8b2","tid":174972,"uid":70369,"like":0,"d